message: Hey guys my name is Victor I created this group so that it would be easier to communicate with everyone. You're more than welcome to say hi and introduce yourself.

I'm Todd.  Graduated in December w/ my MS in Engineering Management at Florida Tech.  BS in Mechanical Engineering.  Considering the heat here in Florida, I'm ready for a climate change...I also imagine I'll eat those words.
